    <mj-include path="../../components/d365-wrapped/wm-hero.mjml" />

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="10px 16px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text css-class="h1" padding="10px 0 0 0">RockStar® Heavy Duty Connectors with SNAP IN Technology</mj-text>
        <mj-text css-class="h2" padding="10px 0 0 0">Install up to 60% faster — without compromising reliability</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="10px 16px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 10px 0">Hi {{FirstName}},</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 10px 0">
          Wiring heavy duty applications shouldn't slow your team down. Weidmuller's RockStar® Heavy Duty Connectors with SNAP IN technology deliver the rugged performance you expect — with a fraction of the assembly time.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 10px 0">
          SNAP IN inserts click into place securely, eliminating tedious screw terminations and reducing installation errors in the field. Whether you're building panels, machinery, or outdoor installations, RockStar® gives you IP65/IP69K protection and vibration resistance in a connector that's built to last.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 10px 0">
          <strong>Key benefits:</strong>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 4px 0">• Up to 60% faster installation with SNAP IN technology</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 4px 0">• Heavy duty housing for demanding industrial environments</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 4px 0">• Modular design — mix power, signal, and data in one connector</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 10px 0">• Tool-free assembly reduces labor costs and rework</mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="0 0 10px 0">Kind regards</mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section background-color="#ffffff" padding="10px 16px">
      <mj-column>
        <mj-button
          background-color="#ef7800"
          color="#ffffff"
          font-size="14px"
          font-family="ARIALNB, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif"
          border-radius="0px"
          inner-padding="12px 24px"
          align="left"
          href="https://www.weidmuller.com"
        >
          Explore RockStar® SNAP IN
        </mj-button>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-raw>
<div data-section="true" class="emptyContainer columns-equal-class wrap-section" style="margin: 0px; background-color: rgb(239, 120, 0);">
<table class="outer" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="640" style="width: 100%; max-width: 640px; display: block; background-color: rgb(239, 120, 0);" role="presentation">
<tbody><tr>
<th class="mobile-padding" style="padding: 10px; background-color: rgb(239, 120, 0);" role="presentation">
<div data-editorblocktype="Text"><h1 style="color: #ffffff; font-family: ARIALNB, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 22px; margin: 0;">See SNAP IN in action</h1></div>
<div data-editorblocktype="Text"><p style="color: #ffffff; font-family: ARIALN, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Request a demo or sample for your next project</p></div>
</th>
</tr></tbody>
</table>
</div>
    </mj-raw>

    <mj-include path="../../components/d365-wrapped/wm-divider.mjml" />

    <mj-raw>
<div data-section="true" class="emptyContainer columns-equal-class wrap-section">
<table class="outer" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="640" style="width: 100%; max-width: 640px; display: block;" role="presentation">
<tbody><tr>
<th class="mobile-padding" style="padding: 10px" role="presentation">
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;" class="containerWrapper tbContainer multi" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
<tbody><tr>
<th data-container="true" class="columnContainer stack-column col-pad-right" data-container-width="60.00" style="vertical-align: top; width: 60%;" role="presentation">
<div data-editorblocktype="Text" style="margin: 10px 10px 4px 0;"><h3>SNAP IN — faster wiring, same RockStar® reliability</h3></div>
<div data-editorblocktype="Text" style="margin: 0 10px 10px 0;"><p>Push-in termination means no tools, no loose screws, and no callbacks. RockStar® Heavy Duty Connectors with SNAP IN are ideal for machine builders, panel shops, and OEMs who need speed without sacrificing IP ratings or vibration resistance.</p></div>
<div data-editorblocktype="Button" class="buttonWrapper"><a class="buttonClass" href="https://www.weidmuller.com" style="display: inline-block; min-height: 44px; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #ef7800; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-family: ARIALNB, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif;">Request a demo</a></div>
</th>
<th data-container="true" class="columnContainer stack-column stack-column-gap col-pad-left" data-container-width="40.00" style="vertical-align: top; width: 40%;" role="presentation">
<div data-editorblocktype="Image" style="margin: 10px;"><div align="Center" class="imageWrapper"><img src="https://assets-eur.mkt.dynamics.com/efac8d96-204d-f011-8ee3-6045bd928f41/digitalassets/images/8a4796b7-109a-f011-b4cb-7c1e52725572?ts=638944025144813367" width="248" style="max-width: 100%; width: 100%; height: auto; display: block;" alt="RockStar Heavy Duty Connector"></div></div>
</th>
</tr></tbody>
</table>
</th>
</tr></tbody>
